metadata.name: Shackled
metadata.description:
Shackled is a self-portrait work about personal unrest and questions in more intimate spaces such as oneself, family, and home. It's kind of a form of self-expression that I'm trying to create visually.

Medium: Printed photograph on photo paper, red thread, and duct tape.

NFT Edition: 1 of 1

Dimensions: 2540 × 3332

Artist: Kurnia Ngayuga Wibowo
